data.description: Adorable traditional style ranch home with basement Large living room and spacious sunny kitchen with island, pantry, lots of cabinet space and dining area. Three bedrooms, 2 baths with a main level bonus room, great for an office or play room. Laundry currently in unheated side porch, hook ups in basement also.  Tons of storage and bonus room in the basement. Enjoy the outdoors, relax on the deck or rear patio, huge backyard for gardening and tons of space for kids to explore and play.  Storage buildings included. Two lots totaling 1.57 acres +/- no survey on file buyer to verify. 6848-66-7467.000 & 6848-66-8636.000 on one deed. No parking issues here! Wide driveway for turnaround too. Home is being sold AS IS seller will make no repairs. See agent only remarks.
